{"tid":2120220,"cid":5,"subCid":10,"title":"★RTHK--英國公布BNO持有人明年起申請5年居留新安排","createTime":"2020-07-22T14:04:04.000Z","updateTime":"2020-07-23T04:40:23.000Z","uid":19454,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":47,"replies":[{"pid":"58a6c875888c53f609234aacff42af4a62c76fcb","tid":2120220,"uid":19454,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:04:04.000Z","msg":"英國政府在網頁公布，申請人可以由明年一月起，申請在英國先逗留30個月、再續期30個月；又或者最長一次過居留5年，期間可以工作或讀書，以及可攜同家屬一同前往英國，但不可領取社會福利及援助。在居留5年後12個月，申請人就可以申請入籍。<br />\n<br />\n申請人須擁有BNO的身份，並不需要現時持有有效BNO護照。條文又要求申請人通常居住在香港、以及有至少6個月的財務支持。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539312-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539312-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&d=DosFxDX7yTzXLN9Gri3QgEoInKkgZqzseva8eQDkMF8%3D&h=4af647a7\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fnews.rthk.hk%2Frthk%2Fch%2Fcomponent%2Fk2%2F1539312-20200722.htm%3FspTabChangeable%3D0&h=971a55a7\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://news.rthk.hk/rthk/ch/component/k2/1539312-20200722.htm?spTabChangeable=0</a>"},{"pid":"fce0282af218a3f6c24e1a41e29e96539ae1041d","tid":2120220,"uid":19454,"like":3,"dislike":48,"score":-45,"citedBy":8,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:04:19.000Z","msg":"但不可領取社會福利及援助<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"91f4332d72b78bb9c7f95d7e0969b881d380df71","tid":2120220,"uid":64303,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:11:29.000Z","msg":"到時有咩大病可唔可以去公立醫院"},{"pid":"ef7c4b86e61229a62bfe26a9f320e0e16025e6d8","tid":2120220,"uid":20473,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-07-22T14:13:29